PREREQUISITES

  You need:
  - A x86 platform or a PowerPC platform
  - 32 MB RAM and 80 MB swap
  - Linux 2.x 
  - SDL 1.2
  - SDL_mixer
  - the GCC C++ compiler
  - GNU make

COMPILING AND INSTALLING

  To install in /usr/local :

       ./bootstrap
       ./configure
        make
        su -c 'make install'

